# OpenModbus Device Registry - Code Owners
#
# This file defines who is responsible for reviewing changes to specific files.
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# === Core Infrastructure ===
# Schema changes require core team approval
/schema/**                              @erikdebruijn @stekker/openmodbus-core

# Tools and CI/CD
/tools/**                               @erikdebruijn @stekker/openmodbus-core
/.github/**                             @erikdebruijn @stekker/openmodbus-core

# Documentation
/docs/**                                @erikdebruijn @stekker/openmodbus-core
/README.md                              @erikdebruijn @stekker/openmodbus-core

# === Device-Specific Maintainers ===
# Each device profile is maintained by its designated maintainer(s)

# Alfen devices
