# Victron devices
/registry/stable/victron/**             @erikdebruijn
/registry/contrib/victron_*.yaml        @erikdebruijn

# === Fallback ===
# All other contrib submissions require core team review
/registry/contrib/**                    @erikdebruijn @stekker/openmodbus-core
